dbtable: (select first("CSN_ID") as visit_id, first("PROC_START_TIME") as tsp, json_build_object('frequency', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'FrequencyOfOrder'), 'priority', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'priority'), 'ORDER_TIME', first("ORDER_TIME"), 'RESULT_TIME', first("RESULT_TIME"), 'ParentOrderTime', first("ParentOrderTime"), 'PROC_START_TIME', first("PROC_START_TIME"), 'PROC_ENDING_TIME', first("PROC_ENDING_TIME"), 'ParentStartTime', first("ParentStartTime"), 'ParentEndingTime', first("ParentEndingTime")) as value from $clarity_workspace."OrderProcs_643" where proc_name ~* 'cpap' or (proc_name ~ 'NON-INVASIVE VENTILATION' and ord_quest_resp ~* 'cpap') group by "INSTNTD_ORDER_ID") A

(select first("CSN_ID") as visit_id, first("PROC_START_TIME") as tsp, json_build_object('frequency', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'FrequencyOfOrder'), 'priority', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'priority'), 'ORDER_TIME', first("ORDER_TIME"), 'RESULT_TIME', first("RESULT_TIME"), 'ParentOrderTime', first("ParentOrderTime"), 'PROC_START_TIME', first("PROC_START_TIME"), 'PROC_ENDING_TIME', first("PROC_ENDING_TIME"), 'ParentStartTime', first("ParentStartTime"), 'ParentEndingTime', first("ParentEndingTime")) as value from $clarity_workspace."OrderProcs_643" where proc_name ~*'bipap' or proc_name = 'HC BIPAP/CPAP' or (proc_name ~ 'NON-INVASIVE VENTILATION' and ord_quest_resp ~* 'bipap') group by "INSTNTD_ORDER_ID") A

(select first("CSN_ID") as visit_id, first("PROC_START_TIME") as tsp, json_build_object('frequency', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'FrequencyOfOrder'), 'priority', first("FrequencyOfOrder"::json->>'priority'), 'ORDER_TIME', first("ORDER_TIME"), 'RESULT_TIME', first("RESULT_TIME"), 'ParentOrderTime', first("ParentOrderTime"), 'PROC_START_TIME', first("PROC_START_TIME"), 'PROC_ENDING_TIME', first("PROC_ENDING_TIME"), 'ParentStartTime', first("ParentStartTime"), 'ParentEndingTime', first("ParentEndingTime")) as value from $clarity_workspace."OrderProcs_643" where proc_name ~ 'MECHANICAL VENTILATION' and not proc_name ~* 'cpap' group by "INSTNTD_ORDER_ID")  as sub
